===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''asbestos'''
# Either of several [[fibrous]] [[mineral]] forms of [[magnesium]] [[silicate]], used for [[fireproof]]ing, [[electrical]] [[insulation]], [[building]] [[materials]], [[brake]] [[lining]]s, and [[chemical]] [[filter]]s; The small [[fibre]]s can cause [[cancer]] when lodged in the [[lungs]]

